  "calculationNotes": [
    "Tax year 2020-2021 with NRB £325,000 and max RNRB £175,000",
    "Gross estate: £100,000 (flat) + £400,000 (other) + £500,000 (to spouse) = £1,000,000",
    "Spouse exemption: £500,000 (fully exempt)",
